snippet.textDisplay:
Really feel niice that finallyyyy Sunidhi Chauhan is here. And, Chhotu khan + the band - what vocalss, loved it❤❤ ❤
But saying that , find such songs' melodies have already became too much common be it in musical arrangements , beat, tunes & also the visual presentation, in all over coke studios now. So this hits no different actually to be honest. So maybe coke studio Bharat creative head group needs to think of new fresh talents from around the country, & make fresh melodies standing in 2024 that will focus on many music scenes of india thats not already covered till now or that much, also focus on how to search for new raw talents (not like that from some making no sense musical reality shows but in literal sense UNIQUE RAW TALENTS from maybe streets of the country to our cherished classical pandits) who can offer fresh Indian taste with the roots of indianess intact, & ofcourse that can only be done if THE CREATIVE HEADS JUST DONT THINK IN A WAY BUT BE OPEN & WIDE IN PERSPECTIVES FOR INCLUSIVITY AND ARE CAPABLE TO DORECT THEM WELL ENOUGH, which somehow I personally find more or less missing in this & previous season too- though the music were ok, but some of the choice of artists felt very typical on focusing on cultures just state wise which were already known to us , instead of unknown or not already covered Indian musical scenes from North east parts,or Southern side, Eastern/Central side including Jharkhand,Orissa, Chhattisgarh, Bihar,Bengal,Indian Island cultures. 
There should be SOME REALLY GOOD VISION on selecting REAL UNIQUE VOICES , TALENTS, artists as a whole, unlike very monotonous , humdrum of Neha kakkar similars, who will be great on presenting the many different cultural sides in beauuutiful way.

 I know Coke studio Bharat can do realllly way wayyyyyyy more in quality and presentation to what its doing right now too. We need moreee inclusive minded talents at the top of the team who can search the unknown gems from the heart of this nation . Good luck CSB👍🏻and much lovee❤
